        ----------------------
        MMS Science Data Center: https://lasp.colorado.edu/mms/sdc/public/
        
        MMS Datasets: https://lasp.colorado.edu/mms/sdc/public/datasets/
        
        MMS - Goddard Space Flight Center: http://mms.gsfc.nasa.gov/
